@Franks laboratory It is too easy to write something like this and forget the braces. alsoDoStuff() gets called in any case.

if(something)
   doThing1();
else
   doThing2();
   alsoDoStuff();

This happens when you are in a rush. It is just better to use braces to make it a code block,  easier to see what is happening.
